{"tid":1112214,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利記煞科戰波飛炒到6000鎊","createTime":"2019-04-17T09:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T15:58:32.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1207a967713406a65f1716dbc2bdb013dd37eb65","tid":1112214,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:51:59.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】英超勁旅利物浦有望奪得聯賽冠軍，煞科戰主場對狼隊的波飛已被炒到接近每張6000鎊！<br />\n<br />\n利物浦現時踢多1場之下，以兩分優勢力壓曼城居首，全力衝擊史上首座聯賽冠軍，利迷歡喜若狂，但荷包肯定要大出血。根據二手波飛網站Live Football Tickets顯示，紅軍主場對狼隊的煞科戰日前已被炒到每張5695鎊，約為5.8萬港元，超過普通打工仔的一個月人工。<br />\n<br />\n諷刺地，該網站顯示最便宜的門票，也要每張600鎊，而官方網站列明主看台最貴的門票，僅為每張59鎊。<br />\n<br />\n炒家猖狂，球會無能為力，紅軍上季殺入歐聯決賽，最便宜的門票由140鎊，炒到1181鎊，球迷組織批評是「炒家所為」，與真粉絲無關。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦周三在歐聯8強次回合鬥波圖，一旦球隊一直晉級到決賽，肯定又掀炒風。<br />\n<br />\n波圖VS利物浦<br />\nNow TV 644台18/04 03:00直播<br />\nNow E 同步直播<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"600d5c43f9dcb2f540e178e77041f2679d12d3a3","tid":1112214,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/SYp7OcljMMN7G/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FSYp7OcljMMN7G%2Fgiphy.gif&h=17f57ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地猁迷希望不會再出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75e8b4d0254728a1316edc6093f4428ef87c119","tid":1112214,"uid":187,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:54:16.000Z","msg":"比6萬入去喊一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1a55a44c19f7fb1ff9a45749f76954282ea849","tid":1112214,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"邊度仲有得買？"},{"pid":"be383d61bc6feccfa3311457e26c01b3c5d15d80","tid":1112214,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re